        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "蓝图评审"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "block-2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "使用这个模板来在实现前评审一份 PRD 或技术方案。"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "id": "block-3",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Context"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "block-4",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "说明这份文档为什么存在，以及这次评审的触发原因。"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "id": "block-5",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Problem"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "block-6",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "描述要解决的用户、产品或技术问题。"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "id": "block-7",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Proposal"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "block-8",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "概括推荐方案，以及它带来的主要变化。"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "id": "block-9",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Tradeoffs"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "block-10",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "说明这个方案刻意没有解决或没有优化的部分。"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "id": "block-11",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Risks"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "block-12",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "列出产品、技术和协作风险，并给出缓解思路。"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "id": "block-13",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Open Questions"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "block-14",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "记录在批准前必须回答的未决问题。"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "id": "block-15",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Decision"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "block-16",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "记录评审结论、负责人和后续动作。"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
